triumph some local sports team?
为最近本地球队的胜绩兴奋吧?

8
00:00:20,770 --> 00:00:23,610
What's wrong with you?
You're freaking me out.
你到底咋了? 这样怪吓人的

9
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:26,970
