distinguished surgical resident at Freemont Memorial.
那女的叫Stephanie Barnett
弗里蒙特医院的有名外科住院医生

22
00:01:19,190 --> 00:01:20,200
Yeah,Leonard told me.
知道 Leonard给我说过的

23
