事实如此 由不得我

29
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,120
Well,aren't you sweet?
难为你了

30
00:01:47,160 --> 00:01:49,620
Anyway,should you have
any interaction with her,
你是不是该和她交流下的?

31
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:54,140
it would be most helpful that
she not see you as a sexual rival.
免得她把你当竞争对手

32
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:58,090
Yeah,I think she's pretty safe.
我觉得她可安全的很咯

33
