You say that now,but consider
the following scenario:
你现在是这样说 但设想下哈

34
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:04,190
You're sitting in your
apartment,it's late,you're alone.
可当你夜深独居闺房 孤枕难眠

35
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:08,570
Your hypothalamus is swimming in
a soup of estrogen and progesterone
雌激素和孕酮刺激你的下丘脑
使你饥渴难耐

36
