Uh,strawberries.
草莓吧

62
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:14,130
Hmm,technically not
a fruit,but all right.
准确的讲不算水果 但还好

63
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,750
Where did you do your
medical internship?
你在哪个医院做实习医生的?

64
00:04:17,780 --> 00:04:19,900
Uh,Lawrence Memorial in Galveston,Texas.
德州加尔维斯顿的劳伦斯医院

65
