70
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:36,250
Radiation burns.
放射线烧伤

71
00:04:36,260 --> 00:04:39,960
A little mishap while I was
building my own CAT scanner.
自制分层造影(CAT)扫描机时
发生了点小事故

72
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:42,810
I'm sorry,you tried to
build your own CAT scanner?
不是吧 你想自制CAT扫描仪?

73
