乖乖 就是这儿了

124
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:25,070
Leonard. Leonard? Leonard?
Leonard

125
00:08:25,430 --> 00:08:29,270
What,Sheldon?
What,Sheldon? What,Sheldon?
干嘛 Sheldon

126
00:08:29,690 --> 00:08:31,320
Tell me what you see here.
告诉我你看到了什么

127
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:35,360
The blunt instrument that will
be the focus of my murder trial?
这笨重的电脑将会是我谋杀你的凶器?

128
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,420
This is Stephanie's Facebook page.
这是Stephanie的Facebook

129
00:08:37,450 --> 00:08:40,670
Now,where it should say "in a
relationship," what does it say?
本该填"恋爱中"的地方 看她写了啥

130
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:42,280
Stephanie Barnett is single.
Stephanie Barnett 单身

131
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:48,120
Yeah,furthermore,earlier this evening,she
threw a digital sheep at some guy named Mike.
没错 还有呢 今晚早些时候
她送了一叫Mike的一只电子宠物羊

132
00:08:49,810 --> 00:08:53,580
Who's Mike? Why does he get
a digital sheep and not you?
Mike是哪根葱 为什么他得到
一只宠物羊而你没有

133
