you? We're losing her.
你眼瞎了吗 我们要失去她了

135
00:09:03,570 --> 00:09:06,450
Okay,I'm going to make
this very simple for you.
这样子 我和你直说了吧

136
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:10,720
You are not in this relationship.
你和她没有什么关系

137
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,920
I am.
我才有

138
00:09:12,930 --> 00:09:19,490
Ergo,you have no say in anything
that happens between me and Stephanie.
所以说 我和Stephanie的事
都轮不到你来插嘴

139
00:09:21,490 --> 00:09:24,500
I'm afraid I can't allow that.
很抱歉 恐怕我不能放任不管

140
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,810
Pursuant to Starfleet
General Order 104,Section A:
根据星际舰队总则104条A款

141
00:09:26,850 --> 00:09:31,030
You are deemed unfit and I hereby
relieve you of your command.
你已经被视为渎职 我因此解除你的职务

142
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:36,900
General Order 104,Section A
does not apply in this situation.
星际舰队总则104条A款
不适用于这个状况

143
00:09:36,920 --> 00:09:38,400
Give me one good reason why not.
给我一个信服的理由 为什么不行

144
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:41,890
Because this is not Star Trek!
因为这不是星际迷航

145
00:09:46,900 --> 00:09:50,880
Penny? Penny? Penny?
Penny Penny Penny

146
00:09:51,510 --> 00:09:52,990
What?
什么事

147
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,980
This is banana bread.
这是香蕉面包

148
00:09:56,960 --> 00:10:00,410
